I'm the Big Guy
Released Nov 10, 2014
For Vince Isoldi nothing is more important than family. Some say he's a gangster, but according to Vince, he's just a good businessman. An entrepreneur with a sordid past, Vince has built an empire in Pittsburgh, from nightclubs to real estate, all in hopes of providing a better life for his family. Now his large Italian-American family is embroiled in a feud that is tearing them apart. Vince is at the forefront so everyone is looking to him for resolution. Meanwhile, his 11-year-old son Adolfo decides to take on the role of businessman and takes over running the family's limousine business.
